  "title": "Freelance Recruitment Officer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Overview</strong><br />We are seeking a motivated and independent Freelance Recruiter to support our hiring needs on an hourly basis. This role offers flexibility while ensuring clear alignment through a paid onboarding briefing conducted in person.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong><br />Attend an in-person paid briefing to understand hiring needs, processes, and tools<br />Schedule and coordinate interviews between candidates and hiring managers<br />Support ad hoc recruitment tasks as required</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong><br /><br />Strong communication and interpersonal skills<br />Able to manage multiple roles and tight timelines<br />Organised, resourceful, and able to work independently<br />Able to attend a one-time in-person briefing (paid)</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>What We Offer</strong><br />$20/hour pay<br />Paid briefing session at the start<br />Flexible WFH freelance arrangement<br /><br /><br /></p>",
